comment.author: 26881258@N07
comment._content: This in flight picture of Marinenummer '695' gives away that it is a Friedrichshafen FF 33h. The h-version was a fighter version of the basic FF 33 with a two bay wing. They were intended for armed patrols. The picture shows the 'flags' near the wingtips, which could mean that this machine was the leader of the group.
